c: 46
v: 15
t: Nos enjoined human est honor his parentes. His mater bore eum arduously dedit genitus to eum arduously took intimate care de eum 30 mensis! When he reaches maturity reaches saeculum de 40 he dictus My Dominus rectus me appreciate blessings Vos bestowed me my parentes perfecit righteous works ut please Vos! Let my infans est righteous alias! Ego repented Vos; ego est submitter